title: The Gluten-Free Italian Vegetarian Kitchen
description:
ISBN: 0399166165 | 2014 | EPUB | 256 pages | 1 MB

From tantalizing appetizers to delicious desserts, The Gluten-Free Italian Vegetarian Kitchen is a collection of authentic Italian dishes with a vegetarian and gluten-free twist.

Made with ingredients that you can find at most local supermarkets, you can use these recipes and advice to prepare healthy meals for any occasion and any time of day
